JAEASortIO input syntax
  bin run input:
    -bin /filepath/runprefix
    or provide one non-.root argument to use as the digitiser run stem.
  event tree output (from bin):
    -tree
    writes the event tree to /filepath/runprefix.root.
    -treepath /path/to/output
    rewrites the event tree output to /path/to/output/runprefix.root.
  event tree input (to hist):
    file.root
    '/path/run*.root'
  histogram output:
    -H / -h
    Build histograms with automated filename
    -hist path/hist.root
    Build histograms with manual path/filename
  particle-ID gates:
    -ID gatefile.root gate_id
    loads the first TCutG found in gatefile.root and associates it with gate_id.
  numeric options:
    -OptionName value
    stores value under OptionName for later access via TestInput/GetInput.
  overwrite:
    -O / -o
    enables overwrite mode.
  calibration file:
    file.cal
  info file:
    file.info
  Info files are expanded inline, and may themselves reference further info files.
Notes:
  If an event tree input includes file.root, matching split files file_1.root, file_2.root, ... are added automatically.
  Duplicate ROOT inputs are removed after wildcard expansion and split-file discovery.
